18:45.958 --> 18:47.918
This is house-made macaroni.

18:48.001 --> 18:50.671
Uh, four varietals of artisanal cheeses,

18:50.754 --> 18:53.841
a Humboldt Fog, a Roquefort, a Taleggio,

18:53.924 --> 18:56.802
and, for a bit of heat,
a Spanish Manchego.

18:56.885 --> 18:58.011
Ooh!

18:58.095 --> 19:01.140
Wow! Gary, I gotta say,
this looks incredible.

19:01.223 --> 19:05.060
Well, I really enjoyed preparing
these bright, bold flavors for you today.

19:05.144 --> 19:08.689
