we didn't know each other that well.

19:48.478 --> 19:52.107
Really? It looked like
you guys were pretty friendly.

19:52.191 --> 19:55.277
We're just close talkers.
I mean, is that illegal now?

19:55.360 --> 19:58.780
She's just some random girl that I went
to summer camp with a long time ago.

19:58.864 --> 20:01.325
We barely know each other.

20:01.408 --> 20:03.452
What are you talking about?

20:03.535 --> 20:06.622
Coop and Katie were, like,
the hot couple last day of '81.

20:06.705 --> 20:08.349
But you knew that.
You must have known that.

20:08.373 --> 20:11.543
- What?
- Wait. Are you kidding?

20:11.627 --> 20:17.132
No. Being obsessed with Katie
was Coop's defining character trait.

20:17.216 --> 20:19.152
But it was a long time ago.
I wouldn't worry about it.

20:19.176 --> 20:20.776
They kissed twice before she dumped him.

20:22.930 --> 20:24.348
