22:34.561 --> 22:37.814
One, two, buckle my shoe.

22:40.776 --> 22:43.820
Three, four, close the door.

22:47.032 --> 22:50.285
Five, six, pick up sticks.

22:51.578 --> 22:53.205
Do you see where I'm going with this?

22:54.956 --> 22:59.419
